# Animations directory

Drop your isometric animation assets here.

Recommended formats:
- hero.mp4 (or .webm) — main hero animation, ratio 5:6
- approach.mp4 — factory schema, ratio 16:10

Usage in components: replace the AnimationSlot placeholder with:

```tsx
<video
  src="/animations/hero.mp4"
  autoPlay
  loop
  muted
  playsInline
  className="h-full w-full object-cover"
/>
```
